5:
*sigh* There's no way I'd be able to 
take on this quest... Or this one either…
9:
Excuse me, miss. Is this the quest 
board?
14:
EEP!
Oh. Erm, wh-who might you be?
18:
Sorry, didn't mean to scare you there. 
I'm still figuring out where everything 
is.
20:
The name's Alk. I guess you could say 
I'm an adventurer of sorts.
24: Oh... I'm Rebecca. A mage... of sorts.
32:
We've just arrived in town, so it's all 
new to us.
45:
F-feel free to ask me any questions
you might have! I'm, um, quite 
experienced with the guild here, 
actually!
46:
Here. You can take on a quest of your 
choice from this bulletin board. 
They're mostly material gathering in 
the Kaleidoscope, but you'll get the 
occasional business opportunity as 
well.
49:
Hmm... For novice adventurers such 
as yourselves, perhaps a quest like 
this one would be suitable.
54:
Hey, this looks pretty doable to me! 
How about it, Light?
58:
...Wait! What about this one? You up 
for a challenge?
61:
Might be too much of a challenge, 
though... What do you think, Rebecca?
65:
Th-that one? Yes, er, it might be a little 
too—
69:
A-actually, allow me to join you! 
Th-that way you'll have a little more 
protection!
75:
O darkness, slumbering in the void—
rise from the shadows!
82:
Whoa... Way to make quick work of 
them, Rebecca!
86: Ehehe... See? I've got your back!
90:
I-I'm a veteran around these parts, 
after all!
93:
I, er, also know a lot about Palpebra, 
so I can answer any q-questions you 
might have!
94:
So um, if you'd like, w-we could maybe 
join—
98:
...?
That's odd. They usually disappear by 
now.
103:
H-hey, what do you think you're 
doing?! Wh-who said you could 
disobey my orders!
112:
I-I'm fine! This is just a shadow I've 
created with—eep!
115: H-hey, cut it out! Get off, get off!
120:
N-not now! Can't you see they're 
watching us?!
125:
Do you usually play with your 
shadows like this?
129:
N-not at all!
Oh, geez... Sorry, but could you please 
do something about this?
133: Ngh... Thank you for your help.
139:
You can count on us to have your 
back too!
143:
Sorry about that... *sigh*
There goes my only chance of making 
a good first impression.
